# Topic 37: UPDATE ⭐⭐⭐⭐

## Why?

Need to correct existing records.

Example

```text
Salary = 50000

↓

Salary = 55000
```

---

## Concept

Updates existing rows.

---

## Theory

Only matching rows are modified.

---

## Architecture

```text
Delta Table
     │
 UPDATE
     │
Updated Rows
```

---

## Syntax

```sql
UPDATE employees
SET salary = 55000
WHERE id = 10;
```

---

## Real-world Use

* Correct customer data
* Update addresses
* Salary revisions

---

## Interview Questions

* Can Delta support UPDATE?
* Why can't Parquet easily support UPDATE?

---

## ETL Usage

Data Corrections

---

## Common Mistake

❌ UPDATE without WHERE clause.

---

# Topic 38: DELETE ⭐⭐⭐⭐

## Why?

Need to remove invalid or old data.

---

## Concept

Deletes matching rows.

---

## Theory

Only matching records are removed.

---

## Architecture

```text
Delta Table
     │
 DELETE
     │
Remaining Data
```

---

## Syntax

```sql
DELETE FROM employees
WHERE id = 10;
```

---

## Real-world Use

* GDPR requests
* Duplicate removal
* Invalid transactions

---

## Interview Questions

* Can Delta delete records?
* Difference between DELETE and TRUNCATE?

---

## ETL Usage

Data Cleansing

---

## Common Mistake

❌ DELETE without WHERE clause.

---

# ⭐ Interview Cheat Sheet

| Command | Purpose              |
| ------- | -------------------- |
