# Topic 39: OPTIMIZE ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

## Why?

Delta writes many small files over time.

Too many small files = slower queries.

---

## Concept

**OPTIMIZE** combines many small files into fewer larger files to improve query performance.

---

## Theory

Before:

```text
1000 Small Files
```

↓

After

```text
20 Large Files
```

Less file overhead = faster reads.

---

## Architecture

```text
Small Files
     │
 OPTIMIZE
     │
Large Files
```

---

## Syntax

```sql
OPTIMIZE sales;
```

---

## Real-world Use

Run periodically after frequent writes.

---

## Interview Questions

* Why use OPTIMIZE?
* Does OPTIMIZE delete data?

---

## ETL Usage

Performance Tuning

---

## Common Mistake

❌ Thinking OPTIMIZE changes business data.

---

# Topic 40: Z-Ordering ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

## Why?

Suppose queries always filter by

```text
Customer_ID
```

Without optimization,

Spark scans unnecessary files.

---

## Concept

Z-Ordering physically organizes data to reduce file scanning.

---

## Theory

Groups similar values together.

Faster filtering.

---

## Architecture

```text
Delta Table
      │
ZORDER BY(Customer_ID)
      │
Better Data Locality
      │
Faster Queries
```

---

## Syntax

```sql
OPTIMIZE sales
ZORDER BY (customer_id);
```

---

## Real-world Use

Large analytical tables.

---

## Interview Questions

* What is ZORDER?
* Difference between OPTIMIZE and ZORDER?

---

## ETL Usage

Analytics Optimization

---

## Common Mistake

❌ Using ZORDER on every column.

---

# Topic 41: VACUUM ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

## Why?

Time Travel keeps old files.

Storage keeps increasing.

---

## Concept

VACUUM removes obsolete files that are no longer needed.

---

## Theory

Old versions remain until retention expires.

VACUUM cleans them.

---

## Architecture

```text
Old Files
      │
   VACUUM
      │
Storage Reduced
```

---

## Syntax

```sql
VACUUM sales;
```

---

## Real-world Use

Storage Cleanup

---

## Interview Questions

* Why use VACUUM?
* Does VACUUM improve performance?

---

## ETL Usage

Storage Maintenance

---

## Common Mistake

❌ Running VACUUM too early can remove files needed for Time Travel.

